---
title: Zucchini Parmigiana with Herby Garlic Ciabatta and Insalata Caprese
description: Parmigiana is a Northern Italian classic. It's traditionally made with fried eggplant but we're using zucchini here for a lighter taste. All the classic flavours remain for a delectable riff on a classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zucchini-parmigiana-86ac8c4f.jpg
